<BaseLayout
	title="Tailor's drawer - astrid"
	description="A compilation of random stuff"
	image=""
	>
	<h1>My tailor's drawer</h1>
	<p>
		There's a Spanish expression called "tailor's drawer" (<a href="https://dle.rae.es/caj%C3%B3n#5mQvJUk">cajón de sastre</a>) used to refer to a messy collection of random items.
	</p>
	<p>
		This page is precisely that, a messy collection of random stuff I have or find interesting.
	</p>
	<h2>Links</h2>
	<h3>Public transit related</h3>
	<p>Most of them are in Catalan</p>
	<ul>
		<li><a href="https://ferroviaria.cat/">Ferroviària.cat</a>, a PWA that tells you the ETA for rail transit in Catalonia (including Rodalies).</li>
		<li><a href="https://www.trenscat.com/">Trenscat.cat</a>, <em>the</em> website about trains in Catalonia.</li>
		
	</ul>
	<h2>Hardware</h2>
	<p>The fact that I'm using this hardware doesn't mean that I recommend it. If I have it, it's probably because it was relatively cheap.</p>
	<h3>Main computer</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>ASUS Vivobook M6500R (it's a laptop I got for relatively cheap)</li>
		<li>CPU: AMD Ryzen 7 6800HS</li>
		<li>GPU: Nvidia GeForce RTX 3050</li>
		<li>RAM: 16 GB</li>
		<li>Storage: 500 GB NVMe SSD</li>
		<li>OS: Windows 11 (I will have to ditch it some day)</li>
		<li>Screen: 15" 2K OLED screen</li>
	</ul>
	<h3>Secondary computer</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Lenovo ThinkCenter M70q</li>
		<li>CPU: Intel Core i5-10400T</li>
		<li>GPU: integrated GPU</li>
		<li>RAM: 8 GB</li>
		<li>Storage: 250 GB NVMe SSD + 500 GB HDD</li>
		<li>OS: Fedora Linux</li>
	</ul>
	<p>
		I found this mini-PC thrown next to a trash container by a random company, and it works quite well. As for the screen, I'm using a refurbished laptop screen, with a controller I bought on AliExpress.
	</p>
	<h3>Phone</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Poco F5</li>
		<li>SoC: Qualcomm Snapdragon 7+ Gen 2</li>
		<li>RAM: 12 GB</li>
		<li>Storage: 256 GB</li>
		<li>OS: Evolution X (based on Lineage OS). Quite stable and smooth, with a ton of features.</li>
		<li>Accessories: Nillkin phone case. It's quite durable NGL.</li>
	</ul>
	<h3>Other stuff</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Camera: Canon EOS 550D with a Canon EF-S 18-55 mm IS II lens. Got it second-hand for cheap, and it's quite good for what I paid for.</li>
		<li>External SSD: SanDisk Portable SSD 1 TB</li>
		<li>Headphones: Baseus H1s</li>
	</ul>
</BaseLayout>